choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Breakfast:
Banana smoothie made with bananas, blueberries, blackberries and a splash of coconut milk.
Oatmeal topped with sliced strawberries and almonds.
Lunch:
Chicken salad made with cooked chicken breast, chopped apples, celery, parsley, lemon juice and olive oil. Served on a bed of mixed greens.
Roasted vegetables such as carrots, potatoes and bell peppers tossed in olive oil and seasoned with salt and pepper.
Dinner:
Grilled salmon served over brown rice or quinoa.
Mixed green salad topped with sliced tomatoes, cucumbers and red onions.
Fruit salad made with mangoes, kiwis, strawberries and blueberries.
